reviewText: Michael Portillo is in love with trains, and his country. This series is beautifully filmed.  I'm in awe of how they were able to shoot everything during England's short 2-week summer.

Sadly it is overpriced by the current seller. I have seen this series of train journies on YT and found it one of the best intelligent and well presented documentaries on railways in the UK. But at the price shown way too rich for me.
